      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Vite默认5173。后端我们定在8080，二进制名叫sbs-backend。两个终端都用subgraph包起来，视觉上清晰一些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReactDev",
        "RustBinary",
        "Terminal 1 - Frontend",
        "Terminal 2 - Backend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把Host Machine画出来，里面嵌套两个终端subgraph，分别放Vite Dev Server和Rust Binary，端口标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Host Machine",
        "Terminal 1 - Frontend",
        "Terminal 2 - Backend",
        "ReactDev",
        "RustBinary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
