      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Browser到Vite的线要标注完整URL，http://localhost:5173。然后关键是Vite到Rust的连接——我们配置了代理，把/solve和/solve-stream请求转发到后端。",
